tel uw droogijs direct bij Orange Nanotech.'),(20460,364,'_page_layout_5_accordion_0_accordion_content','field_5306019b3c6bf'),(20461,364,'page_layout_5_accordion_1_accordion_title','Orange Nano Cryogon Systeem'),(20462,364,'_page_layout_5_accordion_1_accordion_title','field_530601573c6be'),(20463,364,'page_layout_5_accordion_1_accordion_content','Het Orange Nano Cryogon systeem is uniek enerzijds omdat de machine het mogelijk maakt zeer kwetsbare oppervlakken te behandelen, anderzijds omdat de machine een bijzonder goede prijs kwaliteitsverhouding biedt en daarmee droogijsstralen bereikbaar maakt voor een veel grotere groep gebruikers dan voorheen. De machine is kleiner dan veel andere droogijsstraalapparaten, verbruikt minder energie en droogijs, is stiller en nauwkeuriger in gebruik.'),(20464,364,'_page_layout_5_accordion_1_accordion_content','field_5306019b3c6bf'),(20465,364,'page_layout_5_accordion','2'),(20466,364,'_page_layout_5_accordion','field_5306011c3c6bc'),(20467,364,'page_layout_5_background_color',''),(20468,364,'_page_layout_5_background_color','field_5307751fe26ec'),(20469,364,'page_layout','a:6:{i:0;s:11:\"block_icons\";i:1;s:10:\"block_text\";i:2;s:14:\"block_parallax\";i:3;s:15:\"block_accordion\";i:4;s:15:\"block_accordion\";i:5;s:15:\"block_accordion\";}'),(20470,364,'_page_layout','field_5305e90596791'),(20580,365,'_page_layout_4_accordion_5_accordion_content','field_5306019b3c6bf'),(20581,365,'page_layout_4_accordion','6'),(20582,365,'_page_layout_4_accordion','field_5306011c3c6bc'),(20583,365,'page_layout_4_background_color',''),(20584,365,'_page_layout_4_background_color','field_5307751fe26ec'),(20585,365,'page_layout_5_title_reference','Producten  4'),(20586,365,'_page_layout_5_title_reference','field_53062f5a5485a'),(20587,365,'page_layout_5_title','Orange Nano Cryogon'),(20588,365,'_page_layout_5_title','field_53060d758e368'),(20589,365,'page_layout_5_intro',''),(20590,365,'_page_layout_5_intro','field_530600ed3c6ba'),(20591,365,'page_la